es/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2be127ca1b36d3d1e5f9b8ab42549df0536134b","tid":2080554,"uid":352454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T14:23:08.000Z","msg":"笑左，笑埋右"},{"pid":"738634f7f95054fa6feb365091b50c85aa98d264","tid":2080554,"uid":45749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T14:28:49.000Z","msg":"繼兒動母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n柴灣翠灣邨發生風化案。今早8時許，一名15歲姓黃中三男生突然手持一把生果刀，將刀架於正準備出門返工的43歲繼母頸上，並向她胸襲摸下體大肆非禮。黃男其後拿出膠紙有所企圖，繼母奮力掙扎狂叫救命，鄰居聞言趕至喝止。警員接報到場，將黃男拘捕，他報稱糾纏間手部受傷，繼母亦感不適，兩人一併送東區醫院治理。東區警區重案組第二隊接手跟進，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器及非禮拘捕黃男。"},{"pid":"562cf2a73e1c5da0c1bc20e33790e6bc25bd5964","tid":2080554,"uid":3549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e8ff8e5b1b1ee99eb70387ba8c0c81a7de9047","tid":2080554,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T14:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c0b048cbe986637ac0282e7a19fbea1214fbea","tid":2080554,"uid":63124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"靚抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8268a6e94db0a34256484c691cea71caec25456","tid":2080554,"uid":339688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T15:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}